      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Which Brisbane inner east suburbs have the most off-market activity?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Bulimba, Hawthorne, Balmoral and Morningside see consistent off-market and pre-market activity because supply is limited and buyer demand is high. Vendors in these suburbs often prefer a quiet, private sale over a full public campaign." }
    }
  ]
